04:17.700 --> 04:20.010
Hi. What are you doing
on the desk?

04:20.300 --> 04:22.660
Joy Espenson. Get down.
Are you his girlfriend?

04:22.700 --> 04:23.900
No, I just—

04:23.900 --> 04:26.012
