04:37.900 --> 04:40.060
Well, he's 15.
He's going through puberty.

04:40.100 --> 04:41.760
He's starting to get
an acute interest in sex.

04:41.800 --> 04:42.660
Isn't that natural?

04:42.700 --> 04:44.812
And he may be dating
his sister.

04:45.500 --> 04:46.100
What?

04:46.100 --> 04:46.660
You heard me.

04:46.700 --> 04:47.760
But he's an only child.

04:47.800 --> 04:49.660
Well, he is or he isn't.
We don't know.

04:49.700 --> 04:51.860
