groundless, frivolous claims.

06:06.800 --> 06:08.660
He's a big fan
of adjectives.

06:08.700 --> 06:11.160
Yes, I go back a little bit
with wade as well.

06:11.200 --> 06:12.200
Really?

06:12.300 --> 06:14.760
