comtting gross misconduct,

06:14.800 --> 06:16.660
which caused
the victim's death.

06:16.700 --> 06:18.960
But it's a military hospital.
They're immune.

06:19.000 --> 06:22.360
Fine. We have the merits, you
have the legal technicalities.

06:22.400 --> 06:23.660
